Azuwere <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ufeldynn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Feldynn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 66<br> <font color=#E9D756>(3/28/02 5:16:45 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrdragonsandplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3216.topic&index=33>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: To the Members of Endless Prophecy</span><hr size=1> Ok I'm not Trilok or Fystie but .. in answer to your questions Azuwere:-<br>
