What I'd like to know is why we were lied to about a whole bunch of stuff surrounding EP and it's creation, why the whole thing was kept secret and all happened while people were on vacation .. and why did this whole mess between Caelie and the individual rear it's ugly head after 6 months of them not even playing and not broadcasting their return??  <br>
